{"tid":1764622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日起，一齊對身邊嘅黑警及其家人作以下行動 : 咒罵、拒絕、斷交","createTime":"2019-12-01T08:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T11:56:23.000Z","uid":120847,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"417a3b381f7777dea9dd26063689fe757d3aea36","tid":1764622,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地要令每一個警員都被社會摒棄同孤立<br />\n作為社會一員，你有責任<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1.做生意/開舖嘅你，今日起因行政同保安理由，拒絕服務警員，並張貼呢張平安符係門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可保生意興隆，貨如輪轉<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LgZJF7p.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 打工嘅你，迫於無奈要為黑警提供服務時，可以調節一下服務態度質素同效率<br />\n<br />\n3. 有朋友親戚做黑警嘅話，以最惡毒說話咀咒佢同佢地全家，然後同佢立即斷絕來往，並鼓勵其他朋友一同孤立黑警<br />\n<br />\n4. 有小朋友/為人師表嘅你，向小朋友講解黑警嘅暴行，教導佢地明辨是非，並且提防黑警保護自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咒罵、拒絕、斷交</span></span>"},{"pid":"a55c0e847dd374eacccd37a4bc24fb2f601b674d","tid":1764622,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea75eaea1207606cd3355ca1d198d22a69cf2f1","tid":1764622,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0448cd370e7d64c58d239dafd60c2133c53efe1","tid":1764622,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"點解可以冇人理"}]}